OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after cannabis
OL,4,Cplants found next to baby's cot
OL,6,FA drug dealer has been jailed after
OL,7,Fpolice found cannabis plants growing
OL,8,Fnext to a baby's cot.
OL,10,FJames Furlong, 23, first came to
OL,11,Fpolice attention after officers seized
OL,12,Fhis mobile phone which was found to
OL,13,Fcontain messages offering cocaine,
OL,14,Fcrack cocaine, heroin and cannabis for
OL,15,Fsale.
OL,17,FWhen officers then went to his home to
OL,18,Farrest him, in October 2025, they
OL,19,Fdiscovered cannabis plants growing in
OL,20,Fa bedroom cupboard next to a baby's
OL,21,Fcot.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
