OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after cannabis
OL,4,Cplants found next to baby's cot
OL,6,FFurlong, from Huyton, Merseyside, was
OL,7,Fsentenced to three years in prison at
OL,8,FLiverpool Crown Court, after he
OL,9,Fadmitted he production of cannabis,
OL,10,Fand supplying cocaine, heroin, and
OL,11,Fcannabis.
OL,13,FSpeaking after the sentencing,
OL,14,FDetective Chief Inspector Gary
OL,15,FStratton said: "Officers turned up at
OL,16,Fhis home to arrest Furlong for what
OL,17,Fthey'd found on his phone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
