OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782742732
OL,3,CDrug dealer jailed after cannabis
OL,4,Cplants found next to baby's cot
OL,6,F"Despite already being under
OL,7,Finvestigation, you can imagine the
OL,8,Fsurprise when they discovered cannabis
OL,9,Fplants growing in a cupboard next to
OL,10,Fthe cot with cables surrounding it,
OL,11,Fpotentially putting the baby's life in
OL,12,Fdanger of a fire."
